接口 NaiveRedisClient

  • 所有超级接口:

    AbstractRedisClusterClient, SimpleRedisClusterClient, SimpleRedisReplicationClient

    public interface NaiveRedisClient
extends NaiveRedisCountClient, NaiveRedisStorageClient, NaiveRedisSetClient, NaiveRedisSortedSetClient, NaiveRedisGeoClient, NaiveRedisListClient, NaiveRedisHashesClient
    Redis 客户端。可访问以下网站来获得更多 Redis 信息：https://redis.io

    说明：NaiveRedisClient 的实现类必须是线程安全的。
